### Auth 接口测试

### 注册
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "name": "张三"
}

###

### 登录
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

